## 1Ô∏è‚É£ CORE PURPOSE

To automatically **merge same-named `VID_...` folders** from multiple drone cards into **one single VID folder** containing **all files**, with **mandatory user confirmation**, **zero overwrite risk**, and **complete logs**, making stitching fast and error-free.

