## 5Ô∏è‚É£ MAIN FEATURES (HIGH LEVEL)

### A. Folder Selection

* Select **Input Root Folder**
* Select **Output Folder**
* Validation:

  * Input must contain folders
  * Output must be writable
* Clear path display

---

### B. Scan-Only Mode (NO COPY)

* Read-only scan
* Detect parent folders
* Detect all `VID_...` subfolders
* Group folders by VID name
* Count files per source
* Detect filename collisions
* Estimate total size

---

### C. Mandatory User Confirmation (CRITICAL FEATURE)

* Scan Summary Screen
* User must confirm:

  * Input is correct
  * Output is correct
  * Merge behavior understood
* Confirmation checkboxes required
* **Merge button disabled until confirmed**
* Cancel / Rescan options

---

### D. Flat Merge Engine (Core Logic)

* Create one folder per VID
* Copy all files into same folder
* No Card subfolders in output
* Non-destructive copy only (default)

---

### E. Smart Filename Collision Handling

* Auto-rename on collision
* Format:

  ```
  {ParentName}__{OriginalFileName}
  ```
* Applies consistently to:

  * MP4
  * SRT
  * THM
  * LRF
  * Any related files

---

### F. Metadata-Safe Copying

* Preserve file timestamps (created / modified)
* Preserve extensions and casing
* Maintain MP4‚ÄìSRT linkage

---

### G. Live Progress & Status UI

* Overall progress bar
* Per-VID progress
* Current parent being copied
* Cancel / Pause support (optional)

---

### H. Verification After Copy

* Verify copied file counts
* Compare expected vs actual
* Flag missing or failed files
* Continue or stop on error (configurable)

---

### I. Logging System (AUDIT SAFE)

#### 1. Real-Time Log Panel

* Shows:

  * Copy actions
  * Rename events
  * Errors
  * Completion status

#### 2. Persistent Log File

* Saved automatically in output folder
* Includes:

  * Scan summary
  * User confirmation timestamp
  * Per VID results
  * Errors (if any)

---

## 6Ô∏è‚É£ OPTIONAL / PHASE-2 FEATURES (Nice to Have)

### A. Copy Mode Options

* Copy only (default)
* Move after successful merge (locked behind extra confirmation)

---

### B. Duplicate Detection (Advanced)

* Detect identical files using:

  * File size
  * Optional checksum
* Option to skip true duplicates

---

### C. Stitch-Ready Mode

* Auto-sort clips by timestamp
* Optional flat export for editors
* Optional CSV timeline export

---

### D. Presets

* Save common input/output paths
* Quick launch workflows

---

